{"type": "article", "id": 45275, "title": "七匹狼竞购 Bally，以及，回力推出更贵的海外限定版 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-18T03:49:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5806, "name": "回力"}, {"id": 16803, "name": "Pepsi"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 8095, "name": "七匹狼"}, {"id": 7151, "name": "复星国际"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170918100016nNAV9WbR0lHwJdix.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-09-15/china-s-septwolves-fosun-are-said-to-submit-bids-for-bally\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Bally 要卖，七匹狼与复星国际参与竞购</strong></a> | 根据彭博社报道，七匹狼与复兴国际正在竞购 Bally，同时竞购的还有日本贸易公司伊藤忠商事。Bally 于 1851 年在瑞士成立，产品包括奢侈皮鞋、皮带、皮包、钱包和服装。之前曾被美国 TPG 拥有，后者在2008 年将其卖给了 JAB 。JAB 早前称希望专注于食品和饮料业务，决定出售旗下奢侈品牌，之前已把 Jimmy Choo 卖给了 Michael Kors。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2017-09-15/1148095.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>因质量问题，资生堂召回 40 万支眼线胶笔</strong></a> | 上周，资生堂宣布召回约 40 万支眼线胶笔。此次召回的是资生堂 2011 年以后在日本和中国等地销售的“ INTEGRATE Killer Wink Gel Liner”眼线胶笔。据称，该眼线胶笔的部分笔芯混入了塑料容器的碎片，可能会对眼部造成损伤。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.rte.ie/news/business/2017/0915/904904-h-m-trading-update/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 第三季度销售放缓，增幅 5%</strong></a> | 在截止至 8 月 31 日的三个月内，H&amp;M 集团销售额同比上涨 5% 至 74.2 亿美元。该集团表示，因为夏季清理库存的打折活动拖累了业绩增长，完整的季度财报将于 9 月 28 日正式公布。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>庆祝诞生 90 周年，回力推出了海外限定系列<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/wos33-warrior-sneaker-rebranding\" rel=\"nofollow\"> WOS33</a>。首波推出了两款经典配色，白底红标和蓝标，鞋舌缝上了「Warrior 中国上海」球鞋后跟位置分别印上「OS」及「33」。</p><p>这双鞋目前已于<a href=\"http://www.wos33.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"> WOS33 官网</a>发售，定价 70 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105753wionNKHrZAlT1Y27.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181057545mWw68VS1uBZcyjO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181057541LJViqo3ujsdIgTZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105753WexiuapYRBz9l1Oh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181057545CuWkLPMJdZnxaf1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110621XtVjKsbS4GlrB5yv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110621qVyvLINHsMg7ePOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181106211Jwq4xszlNKI7XQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110625sLZ2wlRkqJjFxHoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/raf-simons-dsm-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raf Simons 推出了 Dover Street Market 独占系列</a>，当中的 Walk With Me 红色字样胶带颇为抢眼。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017091810582790uNzvbZtfOILi5r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105828OIskW1T5iFfxoA3y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181058297PMUprWS9XcqxT4F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105829U21RkJpZzaPjt5qO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105832S7DA4X6lispavP0t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181058529wQVHUf1rKyjXni8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/16/bally-collective-swizz-beatz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">瑞士奢侈品牌 Bally 与美国说唱歌手 Swizz Beatz 合作</a>，推出全新艺术家联名系列。 </p><p>该系列灵感来自民谣以及刺青文化，将于 9 月 26 日正式登陆 Bally 官网及各大门店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110031NZH1YqG4QohbS8jy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110027PaWF403Kyr2S6dhM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017091811002771yC2nAwpvl3Ns64.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181100278kuCyRZMa0vnefjG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110027zYI0UHCcteTrau93.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110027mMeui9oC3jEzYW2S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/alexander-wang-x-pepsi-special-edition\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 携手 Pepsi</a>，推出了无糖可乐限量版瓶身。这款限量版可乐瓶只在 <a href=\"http://utc.pepsi.com.cn/pc/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pepsi 官网</a>发售，每天限量 1000 个。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105923DdStcE5O4Ik0HYKZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/opening-ceremony-x-vault-by-vans-authentic-paisley-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Opening Ceremony 与 Vault by Vans 合作</a>，带来了以东方刺绣为灵感的 Paisley 系列，共有 Tango Red 和 Calliste Green 两款配色，每双售价 85 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105939329hN7mEdbnUtLGr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918105940QyNn7mrapofdRExW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Nike 发布全新<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/16/nike-advanced-apparel-exploration-1-0/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> A.A.E（Advanced Apparel Exploration）1.0 机能系列</a>，该系列有追踪身体运动轨迹的热地图技术加持，首波新品包括 9 件单品，售价在 100 至 350 美元之间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110323kMyD0dRUi93E2mPX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110324NzJrK4HVYxEuWBIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709181103268vWLC9z5NASMa4oE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110323wtUAFvDdg78PWKZS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110330zJwSh4r2WA3omTMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110323NQR6yu2IVJntFOGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110323QuTr0MF5x7LklJ4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110323rKFWpEblVXvB5R4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110324EDbxP1y8AWq4gCBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170918110327ni3oqIp8rAblDeT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/wos33-warrior-sneaker-rebranding\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}